Dim tbl As Table
Dim startDate As Date
Dim monthNum As Integer
Dim yearNum As Integer
Dim daysInMonth As Integer
Dim startWeekday As Integer
Dim rowIdx As Integer
Dim colIdx As Integer
Dim dayCounter As Integer
monthNum = InputBox(" (1-12):", "", "1")
yearNum = InputBox(" :", "", "2026")
If monthNum < 1 Or monthNum > 12 Then
MsgBox " !"
Exit Sub
End If
startDate = DateSerial(yearNum, monthNum, 1)
daysInMonth = Day(DateSerial(yearNum, monthNum + 1, 0))
startWeekday = Weekday(startDate, vbMonday)
Selection.EndKey Unit:=wdStory
Selection.TypeParagraph
Selection.TypeParagraph
With Selection
.Font.Size = 22
.Font.Bold = True
.Font.Name = "Times New Roman"
.TypeText Text:=Format(startDate, "mmmm")
.TypeParagraph
.Font.Size = 11
.Font.Bold = False
.Font.Name = "Times New Roman"
.TypeParagraph
End With
Set tbl = ActiveDocument.Tables.Add(Range:=Selection.Range, NumRows:=7, NumColumns:=7)
With tbl
.ApplyStyleHeadingRows = False
.ApplyStyleLastRow = False
.ApplyStyleFirstColumn = False
.ApplyStyleLastColumn = False
.ApplyStyleRowBands = False
.ApplyStyleColumnBands = False
.PreferredWidthType = wdPreferredWidthPoints
.PreferredWidth = InchesToPoints(6.5)
.Rows.Height = InchesToPoints(0.7)
.Rows.HeightRule = wdRowHeightExactly
.Borders(wdBorderTop).LineStyle = wdLineStyleDouble
.Borders(wdBorderTop).LineWidth = wdLineWidth075pt
.Borders(wdBorderBottom).LineStyle = wdLineStyleDouble
.Borders(wdBorderBottom).LineWidth = wdLineWidth075pt
.Borders(wdBorderLeft).LineStyle = wdLineStyleDouble
.Borders(wdBorderLeft).LineWidth = wdLineWidth075pt
.Borders(wdBorderRight).LineStyle = wdLineStyleDouble
.Borders(wdBorderRight).LineWidth = wdLineWidth075pt
.Borders(wdBorderHorizontal).LineStyle = wdLineStyleDashSmallGap
.Borders(wdBorderHorizontal).LineWidth = wdLineWidth025pt
.Borders(wdBorderVertical).LineStyle = wdLineStyleDashSmallGap
.Borders(wdBorderVertical).LineWidth = wdLineWidth025pt
.Rows(1).Shading.BackgroundPatternColor = wdColorGray10
.Rows.Alignment = wdAlignRowCenter
End With
Dim days As Variant
days = Array("", "", "", "", "", "", "")
For colIdx = 1 To 7
With tbl.Cell(1, colIdx).Range
.Text = days(colIdx - 1)
.Font.Size = 14
.Font.Bold = True
.Font.Name = "Times New Roman"
.ParagraphFormat.Alignment = wdAlignParagraphCenter
If colIdx >= 6 Then
.Font.Color = wdColorRed
End If
End With
Next colIdx
rowIdx = 2
dayCounter = 1
colIdx = startWeekday
Do While dayCounter <= daysInMonth
With tbl.Cell(rowIdx, colIdx).Range
.Text = dayCounter
.ParagraphFormat.Alignment = wdAlignParagraphCenter
.Font.Size = 11
.Font.Name = "Times New Roman"
If colIdx >= 6 Then
.Font.Color = wdColorRed
Else
.Font.Color = wdColorBlack
End If
.InsertAfter vbCrLf & vbCrLf
End With
dayCounter = dayCounter + 1
colIdx = colIdx + 1
If colIdx > 7 Then
colIdx = 1
rowIdx = rowIdx + 1
End If
If rowIdx > 7 Then
tbl.Rows.Add
rowIdx = rowIdx + 1
End If
Loop
If startWeekday > 1 Then
For colIdx = 1 To startWeekday - 1
tbl.Cell(2, colIdx).Range.Delete
Next colIdx
End If
For rowIdx = 2 To tbl.Rows.Count
For colIdx = 1 To 7
On Error Resume Next
tbl.Cell(rowIdx, colIdx).Range.ParagraphFormat.Alignment = wdAlignParagraphCenter
On Error GoTo 0
Next colIdx
Next rowIdx
tbl.Rows(1).Borders(wdBorderBottom).LineStyle = wdLineStyleSingle
tbl.Rows(1).Borders(wdBorderBottom).LineWidth = wdLineWidth150pt
Dim filename As String
filename = "__" & Format(startDate, "mmm_yyyy") & ".docx"
End Sub
